Connections from L298 Module to NodeMCU:
- in1 to D1
- in2 to D2
- in3 to D3
- in4 to D4
- 5v to VIN
- Ground to GND

Connections from Battery to L298 Module:
- (+) wire to 12V
- (-) wire to ground

Connections from Relay Module to NodeMCU:
- in1 to D5
- in2 to D6
- Ground to GND
- VCC to 3.3V

Connections from Battery to Relay Module:
- Any one wire to NC terminal
- Any one wire to NO terminal

Setting up the relay module:
- Short the NC and NO terminals of 2 channels
- In the common terminal of the 2 channels, connect the wires from the motor

